title: IHC issues cause list for Justice Tariq Jahangiri’s court
content:
ISLAMABAD, Sep 29 (APP): The Islamabad High Court (IHC) on Monday issued cause list for tomorrow cases in which Justice Tariq Mehmood Jahangir has been included in single and division benches.
The IHC had issued the cause list of the court of Justice Jahangiri after the Supreme Court suspended the verdict of IHC’s division bench which stopped him from performing judicial work.
Justice Tariq Mehmood Jahangiri will hear cases tomorrow in division bench with Justice Saman Raffat Imtiaz. Justice Jahangiri had approached the IHC against the verdict of  division bench.
